{"tid":2362590,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"立即向自己公司提出whatsapp有私隱問題！以此為切入點去令廢中廢老港豬要同我地一齊轉用Signal/tg!","createTime":"2021-01-11T14:13:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T07:05:01.000Z","uid":4322,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"67d0893c5a511e5069386af6ad9acb0dd4029d7a","tid":2362590,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T14:13:59.000Z","msg":"小弟係想大家利用<ins><span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"large\">「WhatsApp有私隱問題 隨時會令公司利益受損」</span></strong></span></ins><br />\n大義懍然咁去鼓勵/迫自己公司改policy！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(理據係最底 驚你地TLDR)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>TLDR: 你(+同事)-&gt;公司-&gt;廢中廢老港豬-&gt;齊齊棄whatsapp! </strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"large\">「好驚公司利益會受損呀」<br />\n「我地傾公事會唔會被Facebook儲埋我地對話架？」<br />\n「會唔會唔小心洩漏公司機密架？」... <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIdeally結果: <br />\n「唔準同事之間用WhatsApp傾公事」</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以此作切入點令廢中廢老港豬去棄用WhatsApp! <br />\n咁都要取代品架？<br />\n最好就推埋Signal (一般對話/gp) &amp; tg (channel/gp)! <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n叻仔既可以扮埋野去compare line/WhatsApp/signal/tg/we7 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最尾你自己寫到signal &amp; tg最叻叻豬就得！<br />\n我唔畀埋template喇 上網大把！<br />\n費事個個一式一樣！<br />\n<br />\n理據：<br />\nWhatsApp某程度上成為左Facebook既私人database <br />\n無錯 佢本身對一般用戶唔收費 <br />\n今時今日 Database=大數據=金蛋<br />\n我目標係令佢隻金蛋變細從而錫佢春袋<br />\n(因為database大細及準確度會直接影響佢廣告點pish點直接賣畀客)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647ab0a9dd251f42743d07342c96ec661692f225","tid":2362590,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T14:14:26.000Z","msg":"Pishhh"},{"pid":"19119180d1857a7b5cdcb1be7046a9522a4915b1","tid":2362590,"uid":79410,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T14:16:42.000Z","msg":"電話係私人嘢. <br />\n正路公司要你用電話做嘢. 係要公司提供埋電話 &amp; sim"},{"pid":"806b5412d9a789375380963a9d889fcfd183839f","tid":2362590,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T14:17:50.000Z","msg":"Pishhh"},{"pid":"958ecaaf4597719d9e31f106a32a79f49ec259b4","tid":2362590,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19119180d1857a7b5cdcb1be7046a9522a4915b1","tid":2362590,"uid":79410,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T14:16:42.000Z","msg":"電話係私人嘢. <br />\n正路公司要你用電話做嘢. 係要公司提供埋電話 &amp; sim"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T14:18:15.000Z","msg":"有幾多中小企會畀呀講真"},{"pid":"b0c2baf3894d7fdd880709f5ceffdb2b08cfd071","tid":2362590,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"958ecaaf4597719d9e31f106a32a79f49ec259b4","tid":2362590,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19119180d1857a7b5cdcb1be7046a9522a4915b1","tid":2362590,"uid":79410,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T14:16:42.000Z","msg":"電話係私人嘢. <br />\n正路公司要你用電話做嘢. 係要公司提供埋電話 &amp; sim"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T14:18:15.000Z","msg":"有幾多中小企會畀呀講真"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T14:20:26.000Z","msg":"我以前間豆腐潤公司. <br />\n真係俾埋電話&amp;SIM 我, 要求我要用公司電話做嘢.<br />\n飛線電話落自己個電話道都話唔得. <br />\n不過我諗佢應該SET 咗定位. 睇住我去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74547c473fb0d159408a9ca808f9d71347198bac","tid":2362590,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislik